schools.name: Don R Daniel Ninth Grade Campus

data.description: This BEAUTIFUL single story, 3 bedroom, 2.5 bath, PLUS flex room is a MUST see!! Exterior is brick structure, landscaped yard to add curb appeal, 2 car garage, & covered porch. Interior boasts of wood, luxury plank, & carpet flooring. Open concept, fire place in living room, granite counter tops in kitchen, large island with sink, eat in kitchen, stainless steel appliances, glass front cabinets and cabinet space, & separate laundry room. Flex room or office. Spacious Owners suite, walk in closet, beautiful bath with 2 vanities, walk in shower, & separate tub. Bonus room for fitness or game room. 2 Additional bedrooms & separate full bath. Out back has a covered patio & private yard with grass.  Just minutes from Downtown Fort Worth, shopping, restaurants, & entertainment. A MUST SEE!
